# Chorum Health: Android-First Healthcare Monitoring Plugin

**Revision 3** — All decisions locked in per user feedback.

Android-first React Native Expo app backed by Chorum's MCP/API. Captures and analyzes health data (Garmin wearable, medical documents, lab results, ICD reports). Shares everything with a web dashboard at chorumai.com/health.

---

## Decisions (Resolved)

| # | Decision | Resolution |
|---|----------|------------|
| 1 | **Framework** | React Native Expo — aligns with future Chorum mobile direction |
| 2 | **Garmin HRV** | Health Connect + unofficial `garmin-connect` lib. Fragile is acceptable. |
| 3 | **TIFF handling** | Server-side TIFF→PNG. Read-only activity — quarterly Medtronic/Epic ICD reports (battery, NSVTs, SVTs, reviewer notes) |
| 4 | **Auth** | Own Google OAuth login page (Supabase Auth), not API token paste |
| 5 | **DB isolation** | Dedicated Supabase branch for health tables. Copy what's needed from Chorum core, maximum isolation. |
| 6 | **PHI in LLM** | De-identified is acceptable — matches research hospital practice |

