**Auth flow:**
1. User opens app → Google OAuth via Supabase Auth
2. Supabase issues JWT → stored in `expo-secure-store`
3. All API calls use JWT in `Authorization: Bearer` header
4. Chorum API validates via existing `authenticate()` in `auth.ts` (session path)
5. Optional biometric re-auth to open app

**Chart strategy:**

| Data Type | Chart | Library |
|-----------|-------|---------|
| Heart Rate | Area chart | `victory-native` |
| HRV | Scatter + trend line | `victory-native` |
| Sleep stages | Stacked bar | `victory-native` |
| Steps | Bar + target line | `victory-native` |
| Lab values | Line + reference band | `victory-native` |
| Activities | Calendar heat map | custom component |
| ICD metrics (NSVT, SVT) | Annotated timeline | custom component |

